00:22:09,058 --> 00:22:13,481
Now, there are 30 to 50 games a day on Steam.

364
00:22:13,481 --> 00:22:19,325
It's a lot more difficult to sell copies of your game in 2018 than it was in 2012.

365
00:22:19,325 --> 00:22:21,787
And you need to be aware of that.

366
00:22:21,787 --> 00:22:28,352
When you are researching, you need to be using recent, modern...

