00:23:14,768 --> 00:23:19,449
Good money, yeah. But then you look into it, and actually

378
00:23:19,449 --> 00:23:22,990
all of these 250,000 copies of this game

379
00:23:22,990 --> 00:23:25,450
were sold at 95% discount.

