00:23:29,564 --> 00:23:33,746
And this is really, really common in the industry today.

382
00:23:33,746 --> 00:23:39,288
So make sure you're being very, very, very careful.

383
00:23:39,288 --> 00:23:41,870
And all the tools that you need to check this exist.

