00:24:18,528 --> 00:24:25,993
Because I have been in this situation before, and I have spoken to indie developers who were told lies.

394
00:24:25,993 --> 00:24:33,358
And they end up signing a contract, believing what they've been told, and they end up losing out.

395
00:24:33,358 --> 00:24:37,161
The publisher does not, but they end up losing out.

396
00:24:37,161 --> 00:24:40,443
Okay? So it's really important to check that stuff.

397
00:24:41,718 --> 00:24:45,481
Always listen to a publisher's research. It's what we're good at.

