00:26:17,599 --> 00:26:21,321
knowledge from these people. And most of them

423
00:26:21,321 --> 00:26:25,023
are very, very, very, very, very, very, very willing to share.

424
00:26:25,023 --> 00:26:27,784
Okay? So make friends.

