00:28:34,485 --> 00:28:38,908
I guarantee that your game will sell X amount, therefore, here's the money now.

456
00:28:41,248 --> 00:28:45,632
We like minimum guarantees. Minimum guarantees are good. It's money.

457
00:28:45,632 --> 00:28:48,274
Recoup percentages are what the publisher

458
00:28:48,274 --> 00:28:52,658
brings back. So for example, if I say I will spend

459
00:28:52,658 --> 00:28:56,302
$10,000 on marketing your game, okay?

460
00:28:56,302 --> 00:29:01,026
When I recoup, that means I take that money back

461
00:29:01,026 --> 00:29:03,428
before you get your money. So if your game

