00:29:03,428 --> 00:29:05,690
only makes $10,000, you don't make any money.

463
00:29:06,985 --> 00:29:12,226
So you need to look into that, and you need to make sure that what's being presented to

464
00:29:12,226 --> 00:29:18,347
you makes sense, and that you're confident that you're going to make money.

465
00:29:18,347 --> 00:29:21,308
To the end of the day, if you don't make money, you don't make any more games.

466
00:29:21,308 --> 00:29:23,948
And that's sad for everybody.

