00:32:59,020 --> 00:33:02,300
to look at this, to think about this,

519
00:33:02,300 --> 00:33:04,601
to turn it over in your head,

520
00:33:04,601 --> 00:33:08,561
because once that contract is signed,

521
00:33:08,561 --> 00:33:09,042
it's done.

522
00:33:09,976 --> 00:33:13,958
There's no going back, that's the point of a contract.

523
00:33:13,958 --> 00:33:17,900
So take your time, don't get too excited,

524
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:20,001
do what you gotta do.

525
00:33:20,001 --> 00:33:24,043
And this is the most important thing

